    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Don&rsquo;t</p>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>use &lt;font&gt; for text style</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>Do</p>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>use css</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>Don&rsquo;t</p>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>use &lt;b&gt; and &lt;i&gt; tags </span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>Do</p>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>use &lt;strong&gt; tag in stead of &lt;b&gt;, &lt;em&gt; tag in stead of &lt;i&gt;, if you want text to be emphasized</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>Don&rsquo;t</p>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>use &lt;table&gt; for layout
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>Do</p>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>use div and css</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>Don&rsquo;t</p>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>user &lt;br&gt; just for white space</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>Do</p>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>use css</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>Do</p>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>Use headings (h1 h2 ...) to indicate the relative importance of text</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>Do</p>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>Use &lt;cite&gt; tag for referencing a book title, newspaper article, or website, and the &lt;address&gt; tag to identify and supply contact information for the author of a page</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>Don&rsquo;t</p>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>overuse &lt;div&gt;tags.</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>Do</p>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>ues &lt;article&gt;, &lt;nav&gt;, &lt;section&gt;, and &lt;footer&gt; tags if needed</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>



]]></content>
